<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Dashboard Producción · CEVIL</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Barlow:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.1/chart.umd.js"></script>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0e0f11;
    --bg2: #14161a;
    --bg3: #1c1f25;
    --bg4: #23272f;
    --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    --border2: rgba(255,255,255,0.13);
    --text: #e8eaf0;
    --text2: #8b90a0;
    --text3: #555a68;
    --accent: #e8b84b;
    --accent2: #c99a2e;
    --green: #4caf7d;
    --green-bg: rgba(76,175,125,0.1);
    --amber: #e8a020;
    --amber-bg: rgba(232,160,32,0.1);
    --red: #e05252;
    --red-bg: rgba(224,82,82,0.1);
    --blue: #5b9cf6;
    --blue-bg: rgba(91,156,246,0.1);
    --teal: #3fc9a0;
    --teal-bg: rgba(63,201,160,0.1);
    --font-head: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    --font-body: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
    --font-mono: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    --radius: 6px;
    --radius-lg: 10px;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  .header {
    background: var(--bg2);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0 32px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    height: 60px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
  }
  .header-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
  .logo-mark {
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #0e0f11;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .header-title {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 17px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .header-sub {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text3);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .header-right {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text3);
  }
  .pulse { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--green); position: relative; }
  .pulse::after {
    content: ''; position: absolute; inset: -3px;
    border-radius: 50%; border: 1px solid var(--green);
    animation: pulse 2s ease-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%{opacity:.8;transform:scale(1)} 100%{opacity:0;transform:scale(2)} }

  /* ── NAV TABS ── */
  .nav {
    background: var(--bg2);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0 32px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
  }
  .nav-tab {
    padding: 14px 22px;
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text3);
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    background: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    position: relative;
    top: 1px;
  }
  .nav-tab:hover { color: var(--text2); }
  .nav-tab.active { color: var(--accent); border-bottom-color: var(--accent); }

  /* ── LAYOUT ── */
  .main { padding: 28px 32px; max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .section { display: none; }
  .section.active { display: block; }

  /* ── SECTION HEADER ── */
  .section-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .section-head-title {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .section-head-sub { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text3); margin-top: 2px; }
  .filter-group { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .filter-btn {
    padding: 5px 14px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    border: 1px solid var(--border2);
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--text3);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }
  .filter-btn:hover { color: var(--text); border-color: var(--border2); }
  .filter-btn.active { background: var(--accent); color: #0e0f11; border-color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; }

  /* ── KPI CARDS ── */
  .kpi-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  @media(max-width:900px){ .kpi-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); } }
  @media(max-width:500px){ .kpi-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .kpi {
    background: var(--bg3);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 18px 20px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .kpi:hover { border-color: var(--border2); }
  .kpi-accent {
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg) var(--radius-lg) 0 0;
  }
  .kpi-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text3);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .kpi-value {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 30px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
  .kpi-meta { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text3); }
  .kpi-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  /* ── CHART CARDS ── */
  .chart-card {
    background: var(--bg3);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 20px 22px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .chart-card:hover { border-color: var(--border2); }
  .chart-top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .chart-title {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .chart-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text3); margin-top: 2px; }
  .legend { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .leg { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--text3); }
  .leg-sq { width: 10px; height: 4px; border-radius: 2px; flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* ── GRID LAYOUTS ── */
  .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  @media(max-width:800px){ .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  @media(max-width:900px){ .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); } }
  @media(max-width:560px){ .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  /* ── TABLE ── */
  .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 12px; }
  thead th {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text3);
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: left;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  tbody td {
    padding: 9px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text2);
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  tbody tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  tbody tr:hover td { background: var(--bg4); }
  .td-date { font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--text3); white-space: nowrap; }
  .td-num { font-family: var(--font-mono); text-align: right; }
  .td-obs { color: var(--text2); font-size: 11px; max-width: 260px; }

  /* ── STATUS BADGES ── */
  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 2px 9px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    font-weight: 500;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .badge-green { background: var(--green-bg); color: var(--green); }
  .badge-amber { background: var(--amber-bg); color: var(--amber); }
  .badge-red { background: var(--red-bg); color: var(--red); }
  .badge-blue { background: var(--blue-bg); color: var(--blue); }
  .badge-teal { background: var(--teal-bg); color: var(--teal); }
  .badge-gray { background: rgba(139,144,160,0.1); color: var(--text3); }

  /* ── MOLDE CARDS ── */
  .molde-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .molde-card {
    background: var(--bg3);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 16px 18px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .molde-card:hover { border-color: var(--border2); }
  .molde-card-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .molde-name { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); line-height: 1; }
  .molde-num { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--text3); margin-top: 2px; }
  .molde-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 12px; }
  .molde-row-label { color: var(--text3); }
  .molde-row-val { font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--text); }
  .weight-bar { margin: 10px 0 6px; }
  .weight-bar-track { background: var(--bg4); border-radius: 3px; height: 4px; margin-top: 5px; overflow: hidden; }
  .weight-bar-fill { height: 4px; border-radius: 3px; transition: width 0.6s ease; }
  .weight-bar-label { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--text3); }
  .molde-obs { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text3); margin-top: 10px; padding-top: 10px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); line-height: 1.5; }
  .molde-date { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--text3); margin-top: 6px; }

  /* ── STAT INLINE ── */
  .stat-row { display: flex; gap: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .stat-inline { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .stat-inline-val { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; }
  .stat-inline-label { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--text3); letter-spacing: 0.06em; }

  /* ── DIVIDER ── */
  .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 20px 0; }

  /* ── ALERT BOX ── */
  .alert {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 1px solid;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .alert-amber { background: rgba(232,160,32,0.06); border-color: rgba(232,160,32,0.25); color: var(--amber); }
  .alert-red { background: rgba(224,82,82,0.06); border-color: rgba(224,82,82,0.25); color: var(--red); }
  .alert-icon { font-size: 14px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
  .alert-text { color: var(--text2); line-height: 1.5; }
  .alert-text strong { color: var(--text); }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  .footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 28px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text3);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  /* ── SCROLLBAR ── */
  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; height: 6px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--bg2); }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--bg4); border-radius: 3px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: var(--border2); }

  /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
  .fade-in { animation: fadeIn 0.35s ease both; }
  @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(8px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); } }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header class="header">
  <div class="header-left">
    <div class="logo-mark">CV</div>
    <div>
      <div class="header-title">DASHBOARD DE PRODUCCIÓN</div>
      <div class="header-sub">CMP CEVIL · PLANTA LAMINADORAS</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="header-right">
    <div class="pulse"></div>
    <span id="clock">—</span>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav class="nav">
  <button class="nav-tab active" onclick="switchTab('estano', this)">Control de Estaño — KLB12</button>
  <button class="nav-tab" onclick="switchTab('moldes', this)">Moldes y Cromado</button>
</nav>

<!-- MAIN -->
<main class="main">

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════
       SECCIÓN 1: CONTROL DE ESTAÑO KLB12
  ══════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section active fade-in" id="sec-estano">

    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <div class="section-head-title">Laminador KLB12 — Control de Estaño</div>
        <div class="section-head-sub">154 registros · Ene 2024 – Mar 2026 · Valores de referencia: Esquina 1,50 mm · Tolerancia 0,10 mm</div>
      </div>
      <div class="filter-group" id="year-filters">
        <button class="filter-btn active" onclick="filterYear('todos',this)">Todos</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterYear('2024',this)">2024</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterYear('2025',this)">2025</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterYear('2026',this)">2026</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- KPIs -->
    <div class="kpi-grid" id="kpis-estano"></div>

    <!-- Gráfico 1: Línea temporal -->
    <div class="chart-card">
      <div class="chart-top">
        <div>
          <div class="chart-title">Evolución de espesores en el tiempo</div>
          <div class="chart-desc">Centro vs Esquina (mm) · Línea roja punteada = diferencia</div>
        </div>
        <div class="legend">
          <div class="leg"><div class="leg-sq" style="background:#5b9cf6;"></div>Centro</div>
          <div class="leg"><div class="leg-sq" style="background:#4caf7d;"></div>Esquina</div>
          <div class="leg"><div class="leg-sq" style="background:#e05252;height:2px;"></div>Diferencia</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="position:relative;width:100%;height:280px;"><canvas id="chartLinea"></canvas></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Gráfico 2+3: Mensual + Distribución -->
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="chart-card" style="margin-bottom:0">
        <div class="chart-top">
          <div>
            <div class="chart-title">Diferencia promedio mensual</div>
            <div class="chart-desc">Promedio y máximo por mes (mm)</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="position:relative;width:100%;height:220px;"><canvas id="chartMensual"></canvas></div>
      </div>
      <div class="chart-card" style="margin-bottom:0">
        <div class="chart-top">
          <div>
            <div class="chart-title">Distribución de diferencias</div>
            <div class="chart-desc">Cantidad de registros por rango (mm)</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="position:relative;width:100%;height:220px;"><canvas id="chartDist"></canvas></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Gráfico 4: Ajustes (vueltas) -->
    <div class="chart-card">
      <div class="chart-top">
        <div>
          <div class="chart-title">Historial de ajustes — vueltas aplicadas</div>
          <div class="chart-desc">Cantidad de vueltas por intervención registrada · Total histórico: 191,5 vueltas</div>
        </div>
        <div class="legend">
          <div class="leg"><div class="leg-sq" style="background:#e8b84b;"></div>Vueltas de ajuste</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="position:relative;width:100%;height:180px;"><canvas id="chartVueltas"></canvas></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tabla de intervenciones -->
    <div class="chart-card">
      <div class="chart-top">
        <div>
          <div class="chart-title">Registro de intervenciones con observaciones</div>
          <div class="chart-desc">Últimas 20 entradas con observación registrada</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="table-wrap">
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Fecha</th>
              <th style="text-align:right">Centro</th>
              <th style="text-align:right">Esquina</th>
              <th style="text-align:right">Dif.</th>
              <th style="text-align:right">Vueltas</th>
              <th style="text-align:right">mm/vuelta</th>
              <th>Observación</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody id="tabla-estano"></tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════
       SECCIÓN 2: MOLDES Y CROMADO
  ══════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section fade-in" id="sec-moldes">

    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <div class="section-head-title">Seguimiento de Moldes y Cromado</div>
        <div class="section-head-sub">CMP Cevil Redondo · 14 moldes activos · Actualizado al 25/03/2026</div>
      </div>
      <div class="filter-group" id="molde-filters">
        <button class="filter-btn active" onclick="filterMoldes('todos',this)">Todos</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterMoldes('Operativo',this)">Operativos</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterMoldes('En calibración',this)">En calibración</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterMoldes('En fabricación',this)">En fabricación</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- KPIs moldes -->
    <div class="kpi-grid" id="kpis-moldes"></div>

    <!-- Alertas -->
    <div id="alertas-moldes"></div>

    <!-- Gráfico peso -->
    <div class="chart-card">
      <div class="chart-top">
        <div>
          <div class="chart-title">Peso promedio vs nominal por molde</div>
          <div class="chart-desc">Verde = dentro del rango óptimo · Naranja = excede el peso nominal</div>
        </div>
        <div class="legend">
          <div class="leg"><div class="leg-sq" style="background:#4caf7d;"></div>Óptimo</div>
          <div class="leg"><div class="leg-sq" style="background:#e8a020;"></div>Excedido</div>
          <div class="leg"><div class="leg-sq" style="background:#555a68;"></div>Sin datos</div>
          <div class="leg"><div class="leg-sq" style="background:rgba(232,184,75,0.3);"></div>Nominal</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="position:relative;width:100%;height:360px;"><canvas id="chartPesos"></canvas></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Gráfico estados + cromado -->
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="chart-card" style="margin-bottom:0">
        <div class="chart-top">
          <div>
            <div class="chart-title">Estado de moldes</div>
            <div class="chart-desc">Distribución por estado operativo</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="position:relative;width:100%;height:200px;"><canvas id="chartEstados"></canvas></div>
      </div>
      <div class="chart-card" style="margin-bottom:0">
        <div class="chart-top">
          <div>
            <div class="chart-title">Estado de cromado</div>
            <div class="chart-desc">Distribución por estado de cromado</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="position:relative;width:100%;height:200px;"><canvas id="chartCromado"></canvas></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Cards individuales -->
    <div class="chart-card" style="margin-top:16px">
      <div class="chart-top">
        <div class="chart-title">Detalle por molde</div>
      </div>
      <div class="molde-grid" id="molde-cards"></div>
    </div>

  </section>

</main>

<footer class="footer">
  Dashboard de Producción · CMP CEVIL · Datos desde Google Sheets · Generado automáticamente
</footer>

<script>
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
